description:
Freely 3d is a set of High quality 3d illustrations of shapes/ objects made in blender.

Freely 3d contains shapes like torus or donut, wired torus, cubes, tetragonal shapes, wired cubes and much more.

this file contains limited objects for now but I'll add more and more objects in near future.

Hope someone will get help with this pack.
